Author: TealNTurquoise
Text: Definitely believe the labeling over the internet. 250 seems far more likely for 8 pieces of sushi than does 150.

Author: bigLlittleL
Text: Most 8 piece sushi rolls have approx 3/4-1c cooked rice (I make my own and yes, it takes this much) plus the avocado so I would say closer to 250 is probably accurate
